# TrailVerse — Frontend Page Map

All routes live under `next-frontend/src/app/` (**~65** `page.jsx` files). Most public pages use `Header` + `Footer`.

**Header nav** (`Header.jsx` + `lib/browseHub.js`):

| Zone | Items |
|------|--------|
| Primary | Explore, Map, Trailie (`/plan-ai`), Blog — plus **Home** (`/home`) when logged in |
| More menu | Events, Compare, **Explore by Activity** → `/discover` (`BROWSE_HUB_NAV_LABEL`; URL stays `/discover` for SEO) |
| More (auth only) | Chat History, Profile |

Footer links **Planning Guides** → `/guides`.

