## Park discovery

### `/explore` — Park grid
- **Files**: `app/explore/ExplorePageClient.jsx`, `explore/layout.jsx`
- **UI**: Search, "National Parks Only" toggle (64), state checkboxes (56), sort, grid/list, pagination, CTA to browse hub (`BROWSE_HUB_CTA_LABEL` → `/discover`)
- **API**: parks list from NPS proxy `GET /api/parks`
- **SEO title pattern**: "Explore All 470+ Parks & Sites..."

### `/parks/[parkCode]` — Park detail (canonical slug URLs)
- **Files**: `app/parks/[parkCode]/page.jsx` (SSR metadata + data), `ParkDetailClient.jsx`
- **URL**: `parkCode` is **slug** when length > 4 (e.g. `yellowstone-national-park`); 4-char codes redirect to slug
- **revalidate**: 300s
- **Hero**: Image, Back, Mark Visited, Favorite, Share, hours summary, phone, official site link
- **Tabs** (query `?tab=`): Overview, Alerts, What to See, Things to Do, Self-Guided Tours, Visitor Centers, Where to Stay, Parking & Access, Amenities, Brochures, Permits, Photos, Videos, Webcams, Reviews (+ Transit if GTFS park)
- **Lazy tab data**: `GET /api/parks/:npsCode/{activities|campgrounds|places|tours|...}` only when tab active
- **Sidebar**: Map, Google Maps, directions, nearby Lodging/Food/Gas/Attractions (GMaps proxy), Crowd Calendar link, Plan with Trailie, Compare, related parks
- **SEO**: `lib/parkSeo.js` — `buildParkMetaDescription`, tier-A parks, state hub links
- **JSON-LD**: injected from page server component

### `/parks/state/[stateCode]` — State aggregation
- **File**: `app/parks/state/[stateCode]/StateParkPageClient.jsx`
- Lists all NPS sites in state (slug like `utah`, `district-of-columbia`)
- Linked from Discover "States" dimension

### `/parks/[parkCode]/activity/[id]` — Single activity detail
- Sub-route for RIDB/NPS activity deep link

### `/compare`
- Side-by-side park comparison
- **API**: `GET|POST /api/parks/compare`, `/compare/summary`

### `/map`
- Full-screen interactive map (Google Maps); loads async ("Loading map...")
- **Layout**: `app/map/layout.jsx`

