## Discover hub (taxonomy browsing)

### `/discover` — Browse hub (taxonomy)
- **Nav label**: "Explore by Activity" (`BROWSE_HUB_*` in `lib/browseHub.js`); **URL** remains `/discover`
- **Files**: `app/discover/page.jsx`, `DiscoverPageClient.jsx`, `discover/layout.jsx`
- **SSR**: `fetchDiscoverCatalog()` → `GET /api/discover/catalog`
- **Sections**: Activities, Type, States, Topics (6 preview cards each, "See all")
- **Search**: `DiscoverSearchBar` — find parks across dimensions

### Full grid pages
| Route | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `/discover/activities` | All activities |
| `/discover/activity/[slug]` | Parks for one activity (e.g. hiking) |
| `/discover/types` | Designation types (Monument, Historic Site, …) |
| `/discover/type/[slug]` | Parks for one designation |
| `/discover/topics` | NPS topics (Animals, Military, …) |
| `/discover/topic/[slug]` | Parks for one topic |
| `/discover/states` | All states/territories |

- **Detail pages**: `DiscoverDetailClient.jsx` — grid of parks, pagination, NPS guide section (`DiscoverNpsGuideSection`)
- **API**: `GET /api/discover/detail?dimension=&slug=`, `/discover/parks`, `/discover/nps-guide`
- **Backend**: `discoverCatalogService`, `server/data/discover-featured.json`

