## Trailie / Plan AI

### `/plan-ai` — Main chat (anonymous or authed)
- **Files**: `app/plan-ai/page.jsx`, `PlanAIContent.jsx`, `plan-ai/layout.jsx`
- **Behavior**: Anonymous chat via `POST /api/ai/chat-anonymous`; logged-in via `POST /api/ai/chat` + `TripPlan` model
- **On login**: migrates anonymous session → `POST /api/auth/migrate-chat` → redirect `/plan-ai/{tripId}?chat=true`
- **Voice**: global `VoiceButton` + realtime session endpoints

### `/plan-ai/[tripId]` — Existing trip
- Sub-routes: `/plan`, `/itinerary`, `/map` under `[tripId]/`
- **API**: `GET|PUT /api/trips/:tripId` (`protect`)

### `/plan-ai/shared/[shareId]` — Public shared trip
- **robots**: disallowed in robots.txt
- **API**: `GET /api/trips/shared/:shareId` (public)

### `/chat-history`
- **Protected** layout (`privatePageRobots`)
- Lists past AI conversations / trips for user

