## Page → primary backend dependencies

| Feature | Endpoints |
|---------|-----------|
| Parks | `/api/parks/*`, `/api/parks/:code/enhanced`, weather, crowd |
| Guides / intent | `/api/parks/search` (traits + match reasons) |
| Discover | `/api/discover/*` |
| Plan AI | `/api/ai/*`, `/api/trips/*` |
| Blog | `/api/blogs/*`, `/api/blogs/:id/comments` |
| Reviews | `/api/reviews/:parkCode` |
| User data | `/api/users/profile`, saved-parks, visited-parks |
| Maps | `/api/gmaps/*` (server-side key) |
| Images | `/api/images/*`, `/uploads/*` |

When adding a **new public page**: add to `sitemap.ts`, set metadata + canonical, decide robots (index vs private), add nav/footer only if product-worthy.
